Using the :zephyr:ref:`Display driver API <display_api>` with chosen display.
That is:

| :hwftlbl-scr:`LCD` : :dts:`chosen { zephyr,display = &lcd_panel; };`
| :hwftlbl-scr:`ST7789V` : :dts:`lcd_panel: &st7789v_240x135 {};`

